Customer Community and Customer Community Plus Support for Asset Lifecycle

With this change, both Customer Community and Customer Community Plus users can see their assets to manage their install base. Customers have read-only access to the Managed Asset Viewer.

This applies to Sales Cloud and Service Cloud in Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions with a Revenue Lifecycle Management license and an Experience Cloud license. It also applies to Aura, LWR, and Visualforce sites accessed through Lightning Experience in the same editions.

Users can access this feature if they can customize customer communities and access components in the Experience Builder or are authenticated external users accessing Asset Lifecycle features.

To enable access, create a custom permission set for Customer Community or Customer Community Plus user licenses. Enable Manage Revenue Lifecycle Management and grant Read access to Assets, Asset State Periods, Orders, and Price Books. Assign the permission set to the user.
title: Customer Community Support for Asset Lifecycle Management
